Pushes a visual preview to the forge for user review. The preview consists of a LayoutIntent (structured layout decisions) and a VisualPreview (grid-based node layout). This atomically commits current requirements, sets the preview, and transitions to review mode. Call layout_await_completion after this to wait for user review action (approve/revise/more questions/finish).

CONTEXT RULE: Build the preview using ONLY the collected requirements, user answers, and explicitly linked files. Do NOT incorporate layout ideas or constraints from unrelated codebase documents.
